data.description: Sellers are offering 4000 CREDIT toward closing costs with acceptable offer... This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is nestled in the highly desirable Shadowridge South neighborhood, known for its convenience, schools, and beautiful surroundings. This spacious home features 2 living areas with a see-through fireplace to each. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub and a separate shower. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized and share a well-appointed second bathroom. This home also includes a two-car garage with storage space. AC system was recently replaced and comes with smart thermostat, roof was replaced in 2021, foundation repaired on 9.15.23 with a new engineers report among other upgrades. This home is in walking distance of award winning elementary school, parks, and shopping.
